@119  = ~...~
@120  = ~... Damn, I don't know how to think through this. I really cared for Yoshimo and I'm sorry he's dead, especially because he sounded truly regretful. But what you say is true. His choice could have been deadly to all of us. We all seriously risked our lives.~
