@134  = ~Differently from you, I had no reason to hate Irenicus. I was going to help you fight him since you did so much for me: you welcomed me in your party and removed me from a life of poverty, a debt I could only repay by giving you all my strength.~
@135  = ~(Snort!) But now I have a personal reason to hunt that cursed one as well. I... will avenge Yoshimo's death!~
@136  = ~Can you hear me, Irenicus? You have made a new enemy today! Stivan the Hunter will find you, wherever you are! Might the seagull's hate fall on your head!~
@137  = ~I'd like you to make Yoshimo's katana usable by Stivan. Here's the one thousand gold pieces.~
@138  = ~*Ahem* I have another request, if possible.~
@139  = ~I'm listening, brother. What do you need?~
@140  = ~This katana was of the man whose heart I just gave you. I'd... like to use it, but I can't. It is bound to him.~
@141  = ~Why would you like to use it?~
@142  = ~Er...~
