@197  = ~The superiority of the female sex is indubitable and requires no discussion, sakphul. Although...~
@198  = ~Lil alerl velve zhah lil velkyn uss. The best knife is the unseen one. Maybe you could give reason to be to your useless life, sakphul, and gut that men without anyone seeing.~
@199  = ~Heh. Anything for dear Viconia!~
@200  = ~Nindyn vel'uss kyorl nind ratha thalra elghinn dal lil alust.~
